(7, 'Samsung 32J4003 32 inch HD Ready LED TV', 'samsung-32j4003-32-inch-hd-ready-led-tv', 0, 'images/portofolio/Samsung40Series5.jpg', '', '<div class=\"sctn prdct-dtl-wdgt prdct-dscrptn\" data-id=\"product-details\">\r\n<div class=\"sctn__hdr clearfix\">\r\n<h3 class=\"sctn__ttl \">Samsung 32J4003 32 Inch HD Ready LED TV Details</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"sctn__inr clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item\">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn \">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-ttl\">Screen size and Panel Technology</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-text\">The Samsung 32J4003 32 inch HD Ready LED TV has been equipped with unique features that provide a cinema hall and stadium-like entertainment experience. The 32-inch screen size displays larger than life images. The slim edge mould with thin Bezel and clear digital view, triple protector and screen capture facility gives a better and sustainable multimedia experience.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item\">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn \">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-ttl\">Refresh Rate and Resolution</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-text\">The television comes with the refresh rate of 50 hertz and contrast ratio of 1000000:1, which avoids sluggishness and renders clear and realistic pictures. It displays good quality of video for viewing and gaming. It has a resolution of 1366 x768 pixels and Wide Color Enhancer for dramatically improved image quality, generating sharp and vivid images.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item\">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn \">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-ttl\">Connectivity Features</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-text\">The Samsung 32J4003 32 inch HD Ready LED is enabled with Connect Share feature through two HDMI ports and two USB ports for externally connecting a variety of devices.  Just connect HDMI-enabled devices, such as the laptop, camera, hard disk and pen drive to these ports and enjoy images and video on the bigger screen.  It also incorporates audio output to create the instant entertainment centre.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item\">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn \">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-ttl\">Audio Features</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-text\">The television audio has been perfected with excellent sound quality through Dolby Digital Plus sound system and two inbuilt speakers that output a total of 10 Watts of RMS.and down firing bass reflex ability. It is also integrated with additional audio features that include Virtual Surround- DTS Studio Sound and DTS Codec - DTS Premium Sound Wall Mount Sound Mode Sound Capture.  In all, audio features give best entertainment experience.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item\">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn \">\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-ttl\">Other Exciting Features</div>\r\n<div class=\"prdct-dscrptn__item-text\">The Samsung 32J4003 features some unique modes such as Indian Cinema Mode and Cricket Mode that can be enjoyed in any preferred language with OSD language support, all day long with minimum power consumption of 48 Watts. Grab yours online at the lowest price by checking out our best offers. </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"sctn sctn--no-pdng tchncl-spcftn clearfix\" data-id=\"technical-specifications\">\r\n<h2 class=\"sctn__hdr prc-grid__hdr\">Samsung 32J4003 32 Inch HD Ready LED TV Specifications</h2>\r\n<div class=\"tchncl-spcftn__tbl-wrpr\">\r\n<h4 class=\"tchncl-spcftn__cptn\">GENERAL</h4>\r\n<table class=\"tchncl-spcftn__tbl\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Brand</td>\r\n<td>Samsung</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Model No</td>\r\n<td>32J4003</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Smart TV</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tchncl-spcftn__tbl-wrpr\">\r\n<h4 cl